# Normalize line endings: store text as LF in the repo and check out LF on every
# platform. Prevents CRLF working trees on Windows (Git-for-Windows defaults
# core.autocrlf=true) from drifting against the LF-normalized repo + CI.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Explicit binary types (also auto-detected, but pinned for safety).
*.jar binary
*.ico binary
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
